oai_dc:dc.dc:title: New golf club at Shelby Park, Nashville, Tennessee, 1960 February 08
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: A photo related to the new golf club at Nashville’s Shelby Park, February 8, 1960. Located in historic East Nashville, Shelby Golf Course opened in 1924. It has the distinction of being the first municipal golf course in Nashville, Tennessee. Forms part of Record Group 3, Metro Davidson County Photographer. 1 photograph negative : b & w ; 4 x 5 in.
